{"tid":1434411,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有無前學聯人出黎講下 差佬出反對通知書代表D咩?","createTime":"2019-08-08T18:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T20:04:45.000Z","uid":96868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8497791ab8218db1ebc7d42865f2762832c7c156","tid":1434411,"uid":96868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:41:45.000Z","msg":"學聯雖然收左皮<br />\n不過大專學界既力量係不容忽視, 反送中到而家大學生付出左好多<br />\n我聽朋友個朋友講, 佢以前上過學聯<br />\n佢話學聯<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從來都無</span></span>向警方申請遊行不反對通知書。<br />\n每次都有狗跟住但唔敢搞鳩佢地<br />\n<br />\n到底堅唔堅?<br />\n如果係堅既, 我屌, 而家2019 香港人咪仲縮過以前???????????<br />\n大埔遊行 機埸集會 黃大仙遊行<br />\n全部反對哂, 你地就唔去????????<br />\n咁政府話要送中, 我地點解要反對? 反正我地都係聽政府講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3cee731c8cbc07267efc2b079134e072c08ed5","tid":1434411,"uid":96868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:42:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7124dcde1e8907b3d740b31bb8092defda43b890","tid":1434411,"uid":96868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:45:08.000Z","msg":"推到有人回我"},{"pid":"3177c73a1b1d2d7d8538622a066b75f2ef99d315","tid":1434411,"uid":2769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:46:58.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"5fd57ccfdbd3488d24bb9763f6bba2c868830f64","tid":1434411,"uid":96868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:59:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3842455d18bc27bc5eb8e576154bd529ed65dc5","tid":1434411,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:02:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷至今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、 成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</span>"},{"pid":"7cdbe38a390f4b9f10fa066303ec50714c110f91","tid":1434411,"uid":1712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:04:47.000Z","msg":"因為學聯既活動一定好和平囉<br />\n有人想有稍為激烈啲既動作，都俾